## 🚀 Getting Started (Phase MVP Deliverables Ready):
```bash
cd labs/path-1-sovereign-foundations/chapter-jwt-auth
docker compose up -d --build docker-compose.yml.example  

# Expected Output: Backend service running on port 8080 with health checks ready from Phase 0 MVP deliverable specs.  
curl http://localhost:8080/health

