## 🛡️ Security Hardening Applied Throughout (from v1.2 upgrade docs Section 4):
All Docker Compose configurations include security_opt flags ready for enterprise tier deployment as specified in Phase MVP deliverable requirements:
```yaml  
security_opt: 
    - no-new-privileges:true     
      - apparmor=unconfined        # Enterprise tier optional

cap_drop:    
  - ALL                         # Drop all capabilities; add back selectively  

user_namespace_isolation_enabled = true (UID:${GID} mapping)  
```

